{"tid":1566911,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我係外國撚，但係9月15號，可唔可以見翻200萬香港人","createTime":"2019-09-13T20:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T23:31:52.000Z","uid":23480,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0de41beb420b5ea0740b5b157c78d0a5d3af5b2","tid":1566911,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T20:47:09.000Z","msg":"我係外國撚，你可以叫我冷氣軍師，又或者逃兵，點稱呼我都可以。但係我想跪求香港人做一件事，就係一齊行上街同全世界，同香港政府，同共產黨講THIS IS NOT THE END. 我地要五大訴求，十幾條人命，千幾人被捕，兄弟手足受傷無數，兩次既恐怖襲擊，全部都要共產黨還。我知我無資格叫大家做任何野，但係呢一次，真心NOW OR NEVER，香港唔可以輸，香港人唔可以輸，輸左我地將一無所有。<br />\n<br />\nHONG KONG EXPECT EVERYONE DO HIS/HER DUTY. <br />\n<br />\n我想跪求大家。<br />\n9月15日<br />\n全香港人，由自己屋企出發，行上去禮賓府，一齊唱榮光，唱到柒婆肯答應哂五大訴求為止，再一齊係煲底相認，齊齊整整，一齊拯救香港。<br />\n<br />\n時代革命，光復香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/feMQpLg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfeMQpLg.jpg&h=314071d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RRE6HwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRRE6HwY.jpg&h=c1d479c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f496d8895d05b64192e48e083746ee577edb603","tid":1566911,"uid":120555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T20:50:54.000Z","msg":"難啲 但10月1應該見到"},{"pid":"53b649e1811b949c89841a135159add08998c752","tid":1566911,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T22:09:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8b04a47c323c3747c4882e1cf89ddd8dcf0869c","tid":1566911,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T23:30:29.000Z","msg":"我要200萬人"},{"pid":"b6dd83c8df6cbcb252c7ecb53e0cac17c0dd8232","tid":1566911,"uid":133453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T23:31:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}